        <para>Note: An edited volume can be part of a series, just like a book. You can have a contribution contained in an edited volume contained in a
            series etc.. Make sure you structure your entry accordingly.</para>
        <para> The Basic Input Forms accommodate these types of bibliographical entries (and a few more). You can create new forms for specific purposes, for example, to accommodate more bibliographical types or to meet the needs of specific projects.</para>
